WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.867 --> 00:00:02.168
- Oh, this train's
coming right at me.

00:00:02.201 --> 00:00:04.170
That's incredible.

00:00:04.203 --> 00:00:05.238
Oh, my God! Oh!

00:00:05.271 --> 00:00:06.839 align:start position:0%
[yelling]

00:00:06.872 --> 00:00:08.608 align:end position:100%
- What have you done
with the morphine room?

00:00:08.641 --> 00:00:10.109 align:start position:0%
- This is my dojo.

00:00:10.142 --> 00:00:12.011
Pause.
- I know what you're doing,

00:00:12.044 --> 00:00:14.113
Father Donahue, and I demand
that you stop taking advantage

00:00:14.146 --> 00:00:16.516 align:end position:100%
of Lady Dodo's kind heart
and generosity.

00:00:16.549 --> 00:00:20.219
- Or what?
- Or feel the full wrath

00:00:20.252 --> 00:00:21.721 align:start size:47% position:53%
of Mr. Peepers.

00:00:21.754 --> 00:00:23.556 size:78% position:39%
- All right, Mr. Peepers.

00:00:23.589 --> 00:00:25.158 align:start position:0%
Let me feel this wrath.

00:00:25.191 --> 00:00:27.227
<i> [guitar note resonates]</i>

00:00:31.730 --> 00:00:33.699 align:start size:28% position:72%
- A duel.

00:00:33.732 --> 00:00:35.701 align:start position:0%
- A duel it is.

00:00:35.734 --> 00:00:37.270 align:start position:0%
To the death.

00:00:37.303 --> 00:00:38.605 align:start position:0%
Artistically speaking.

00:00:40.973 --> 00:00:42.275 align:start position:0%
- [blowing]

00:00:42.308 --> 00:00:44.043 align:start position:0%
Warm my fingers,
please, Garfield.

00:00:44.076 --> 00:00:45.378 align:end position:100%
- Do you have one
of those glass things

00:00:45.411 --> 00:00:46.779 align:start size:72% position:28%
you put on your finger?

00:00:46.812 --> 00:00:48.381 align:start position:0%
- The duel was under
your initiation.

00:00:48.414 --> 00:00:49.682
You begin.
- Fine.

00:00:49.715 --> 00:00:52.152
Garfield, give us a C, please.

00:00:53.752 --> 00:00:55.154
- [hums note]

00:00:55.187 --> 00:00:57.156
[both strumming]
- Ooh, that's off.

00:00:57.189 --> 00:00:58.624
That's off, isn't it?
- Yes.

00:00:58.657 --> 00:01:01.060 size:88% position:44%
- We'll just try that again.

00:01:01.093 --> 00:01:02.462
[strumming tune]

00:01:02.495 --> 00:01:03.629 align:start position:0%
It's probably easier
if I tune to you.

00:01:03.662 --> 00:01:04.630
- Fine.

00:01:04.663 --> 00:01:07.567
[both strumming]

00:01:07.600 --> 00:01:09.235 align:start position:0%
[humming]

00:01:09.268 --> 00:01:11.504
- Does that sound okay?
- [humming]

00:01:11.537 --> 00:01:13.005
What note is that?
- I don't know.

00:01:13.038 --> 00:01:14.841 align:start position:0%
- Do you know,
"Oh, He's My Savior,

00:01:14.874 --> 00:01:16.843
Let Him Come Amongst Us"?
- Do you have a tuning fork?

00:01:16.876 --> 00:01:18.845 align:start position:0%
- Do you know,
"Oh, Christ, Here He Is"?

00:01:18.878 --> 00:01:20.746
- Do you know "Camptown Races"?

00:01:20.779 --> 00:01:22.982 size:88% position:44%
- Do you know, "Oh, Gay Are
The Days For He Is The One"?

00:01:23.015 --> 00:01:24.984 align:end position:100%
- Do you know, "Champagne
Charlie Was His Name"?

00:01:25.017 --> 00:01:26.619 align:start position:0%
- How does that go?

00:01:26.652 --> 00:01:28.621
Is that--
- ♪ Champagne Charlie ♪

00:01:28.654 --> 00:01:30.356
[both singing]
- Are you alone?

00:01:32.591 --> 00:01:34.127
- Does it look like I'm alone?

00:01:34.160 --> 00:01:35.628 align:start size:19% position:81%
- Yes.

00:01:35.661 --> 00:01:37.396 align:start position:0%
- There are two other men
in this room.

00:01:37.429 --> 00:01:38.898 align:end position:100%
- Yes, but I always
[bleep] in front of them.

00:01:38.931 --> 00:01:40.399
- It's true.

00:01:40.432 --> 00:01:43.236 size:88% position:56%
- I've been very bad, Padre.

00:01:43.269 --> 00:01:46.239 align:start size:78% position:22%
You may need to spank me.

00:01:46.272 --> 00:01:48.141
- Frederick.
- Mmm?

00:01:48.174 --> 00:01:50.576 align:start position:0%
- I will never,
ever make love to you.

00:01:50.609 --> 00:01:52.578 align:start position:0%
Ever.

00:01:52.611 --> 00:01:55.581 align:start size:34% position:66%
- [sobbing]

00:01:55.614 --> 00:01:58.417 align:start size:50% position:50%
- We'll continue
this later, sir.

00:01:58.450 --> 00:02:01.120 align:start position:0%
- Don't get on
my bad side, Peepers.

00:02:01.153 --> 00:02:03.122 align:start position:0%
I intend to be here

00:02:03.155 --> 00:02:05.058 align:start position:0%
for a very long time.

